author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
One of the great special effects films of the mid-20th century is Jason and the Argonauts, featuring the groundbreaking stop-motion creatures of Ray Harryhausen. At Propstore, Adam rediscovers his love for the film by wielding some of its real metal weapon and armor props, as well as examining a piece of original Harryhausen concept art!

Learn more about this prop and see more details at: https://propstoreauction.com/auctions/info/id/462
Original Ray Harryhausen Stop-Motion Creatures: https://youtu.be/2AzLzJKWJHc

Shot by Josh Self and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
